{
  "id": "RAW_98ce75f5",
  "title": "Chat SDK 现已推出适配器目录 - Vercel",
  "url": "https://vercel.com/changelog/chat-sdk-adapter-directory",
  "date": "2026-03-10 13:00:00",
  "author": "Hayden Bleasel, Ben Sabic",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__9eLiuW__content\">\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Chat SDK now has a new <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/adapters\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/adapters\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">adapter directory</a>, so you can search platform and state adapters from Vercel and the community.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">These include:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Official</b> adapters: maintained the core Chat SDK team and published under <code>@chat-adapter/*</code></p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Vendor-official</b> adapters: built and maintained by the platform companies, like <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/adapters/resend\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/adapters/resend\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Resend</a><a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/adapters/resend\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/adapters/resend\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">'s email</a>, <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/adapters/matrix\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/adapters/matrix\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Beeper Matrix</a>, and <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/adapters/imessage\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/adapters/imessage\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Photon iMessage</a>. These live in the vendor's GitHub org and are documented in their docs.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Community</b> adapters are built by third-party developers, and can be published by one, following the same model as <a href=\"https://ai-sdk.dev/providers/community-providers\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://ai-sdk.dev/providers/community-providers\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">AI SDK community providers</a>.</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">We encourage teams to build and submit adapters to be included in this new directory and made available to the community, like Resend's adapter that connects email to Chat SDK:</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-javascript code-block-module__NOThwW__pre blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__maxHeight\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token imports\"> </span><span class=\"token imports maybe-class-name\">Chat</span><span class=\"token imports\"> </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"chat\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token imports\"> </span><span class=\"token imports maybe-class-name\">MemoryStateAdapter</span><span class=\"token imports\"> </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"@chat-adapter/state-memory\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token imports\"> createResendAdapter </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"@resend/chat-sdk-adapter\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L5\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> resend </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">createResendAdapter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L6\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">fromAddress</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"bot@yourdomain.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L7\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L8\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L9\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> chat </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token class-name\">Chat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L10\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">userName</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"email-bot\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L11\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">adapters</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> resend </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L12\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">state</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token class-name\">MemoryStateAdapter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L13\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L14\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L15\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token comment\">// New inbound email (new thread)</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L16\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">chat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">onNewMention</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">async</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">thread</span><span class=\"token parameter punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token parameter\"> message</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token arrow operator\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L17\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> thread</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">subscribe</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L18\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> thread</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">post</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token template-string string\">Got your email: </span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation\">message</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation property-access\">text</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C34a68e73-L19\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Browse the <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/adapters\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/adapters\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">adapter directory</a> or read the <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/docs/contributing/building\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/docs/contributing/building\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">contributing guide</a> to learn how to build, test, document, and publish your own adapter.</p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel 为其 Chat SDK 推出了一个中心化的适配器目录，对官方、厂商和社区构建的集成进行了分类，以简化多平台聊天开发。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel 为其 Chat SDK 推出了一个中心化的适配器目录，对官方、厂商和社区构建的集成进行了分类，以简化多平台聊天开发。",
  "summary": "Vercel 宣布为其 Chat SDK 推出全新的适配器目录，旨在帮助开发者轻松查找和实现平台及状态适配器。该目录将这些工具分为三个不同的类别：由 Vercel 维护的官方适配器、由 Resend 和 Matrix 等合作伙伴公司构建的厂商官方适配器，以及由第三方开发者创建的社区适配器。文章通过提供邮件转聊天集成的代码片段，强调了 Chat SDK 的可扩展性，并鼓励开发者参考提供的文档和贡献指南贡献自己的适配器。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Vercel 引入了结构化目录，以集中化 Chat SDK 适配器的发现过程。",
      "explanation": "这一新资源允许开发者搜索平台和状态适配器，显著减少了集成各种通信渠道和存储后端时的阻力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "生态系统分为官方、厂商官方和社区贡献三个层级，以确保清晰度。",
      "explanation": "通过根据维护者对适配器进行分类，Vercel 让开发者对所选集成工具的支持、文档和可靠性有了明确的预期。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该计划鼓励通过社区驱动的方式来扩展 Chat SDK 的功能。",
      "explanation": "Vercel 提供了全面的贡献指南和代码示例，赋能开发者和厂商构建、测试并发布自己的适配器，从而培育更丰富的集成生态系统。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Chat SDK 现在有了新的适配器目录，因此你可以搜索来自 Vercel 和社区的平台及状态适配器。",
    "官方适配器：由 Chat SDK 核心团队维护，并以 @chat-adapter/* 命名发布。",
    "我们鼓励团队构建并提交适配器，将其纳入这个新目录并提供给社区使用。"
  ],
